FBIS3-31897 "dreeu039_c_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Havel `Deeply Shaken' by Hebron Massacre LD2602174294 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network in Czech 1600 GMT 26 Feb 94 LD2602174294 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network Language: Czech Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] President of the Republic Vaclav Havel is deeply shaken and outraged by the massacre in Hebron. [passage omitted] Vaclav Havel hopes that Israeli authorities will investigate the incident and that they will draw tough conclusions and introduce security measures. The Czech president believes that this tragic event will not jeopardize the continuation of peace talks between the PLO and Israel.
